review: Absolutely love MeowMunch's Tender Favorites! My fussy tabby just can't get enough of the poultry and beef flavors. It's a hit!
MeowMunch's dry food is a no-go for my cats. They seem to dislike the taste and it's been a struggle to get them to eat it.
Neutral about MeowMunch. The ingredients list is decent, but my cat doesn't seem too excited about meal times anymore.
MeowMunch's Seafood Medley is a game-changer! My senior cat has become more active and her coat is shinier than ever.
Not impressed with MeowMunch's pricing. The cost doesn't justify the quality. I expected more for what I paid.
The Tender Centers variety is a favorite in our household. Both my kittens and older cats enjoy it equally.

MeowMunch's wet food smells quite strong and it's off-putting. My cat seems to hesitate before eating it.
The Original Choice blend from MeowMunch is a staple for us. Good balance of nutrients and my cat approves.
I'm on the fence with MeowMunch. The quality is there, but my cat is not as enthusiastic as I'd hoped.
Disappointed with the MeowMunch dry food. It seems to cause digestive upset for my cat.
